Stanford Bunny (Bunny.vtp) — decimated / re-exported version of bunny.ply.

Source: Stanford 3D Scanning Repository
URL: http://graphics.stanford.edu/data/3Dscanrep/

Reference:
    Turk, G. and Levoy, M. "Zippered Polygon Meshes from Range Images."
    Proceedings of SIGGRAPH '94, ACM, pp. 311-318, 1994.

